Notes:
Trey teased San-Ho-Zay during Weekapaug and teased Crosseyed during Steam, Piper, Light, First Tube and Walls of The Cave. Piper featured Trey on Marimba Lumina and all four band members playing Fishman's drum kit with jamming that included Crosseyed quotes. Light, First Tube, and Walls Of The Cave also included Crosseyed quotes
